{"tid":1285445,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"教大悼念同路人...","createTime":"2019-07-04T14:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T14:49:02.000Z","uid":267137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c57f8819a11e8ef0eb36938333937c384a97eb88","tid":1285445,"uid":267137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:42:43.000Z","msg":"教大星期六有悼念...<br />\n原來鄔小姐都係教大校友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-轉-<br />\n<br />\n對於近日接二連三的不幸事件，本會感到十分沉重悲痛。明天是盧同學頭七的日子。與此同時，本會已證實，另一位同路人鄔小姐亦是本校校友。<br />\n<br />\n面對我們的同學以及師姐的離去，或許我們內心感到無力、憤怒、失落，但需知道抗爭道路漫長。此時此刻，我們要堅強，我們一個都不能少。因此，本會聯同一群已畢業的香港教育大學學生發起悼念活動，邀請所有教大師生、校友、教職員，以及香港市民出席。願兩位死者安息，同時身邊朋友和家屬能早日走出傷痛。<br />\n<br />\n悼念活動詳情：<br />\n日期：七月六日（星期六）<br />\n時間：下午三時<br />\n地點：香港教育大學中央廣場<br />\n<br />\n我們亦僅此呼籲各位如有情緒問題，請務必向身邊人求助，亦可向不同機構尋求情緒支援。"},{"pid":"3aeff50da9dbc353b03cce417f0de8732ffe8afe","tid":1285445,"uid":267137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:44:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f985c9b595b2f1db09531f4651cef020269a7cdb","tid":1285445,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a916b3bc3c545e62e4207f761b5fb0727ef4a288","tid":1285445,"uid":267137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:49:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}